All data in this file relates to simulations conducted in maize & rice. Each mutant (ie ddm1, zmet2, fancm recq4, 10X, ddm1/zmet2) has its own .R file with the construction of genetic maps.
Code for simulations ran (both recurrent selection & introgression) are in intermating & introgression marked files.
Loci positions used for the polygenic trait for both maize and rice are in .RData files since they were randomly sampled. Genetic maps used are also avaliable in .RData files but not the recombination data used to generate them.
Code related to correlating gene density & recombination rate is in gene density .R file. 

If you have questions email rke27@cornell.edu.
